title.rendered: Ice Cool Gel Pad 5cm x 12, Pack of 10

content.rendered:
Cold Therapy Gel Pad

• Cool & soothing effect for a wide range of applications
• Stays cool for up 8 hours
• No icing or refrigeration required
• Gently adheres to injury site
• No taping required
